Act or omission done in good faith
40. No action or suit shall be instituted or maintained in any court
against—
(a) the Board;
(b) a member of the Board;
(c) the Rector;
(d) the Deputy Rector;
(e) the Registrar;
(f) the Bursar;
(g) the Board of Studies;
(h) a member of the Board of Studies;
(i) a staff of the Akademi; and
(j) a person authorized to act for or on behalf of any of the
bodies or persons under paragraphs (a) to (i),
for any act or omission done in good faith in the exercise or
discharge of its or his powers or duties under this Act in a reasonable
belief that it was necessary for the purpose intended to be served
thereby.
